choices.text:
Put together a healthy meal plan for me for 7 days.  I can't have dairy, garlic, honey, almonds, pistachios, or cashews
Day 1: Oatmeal with fresh fruit and nuts (such as walnuts)
Day 2: Quinoa salad with grilled chicken and vegetables
Day 3: Lentil soup with whole wheat bread
Day 4: Grilled tofu with roasted vegetables
Day 5: Brown rice stir-fry with veggies and a side of quinoa
Day 6: Baked salmon with sweet potato mash
Day 7: Chickpea curry with brown rice
